videos.description: Off the pick and roll, Bruno Fernando charges down the paint, catches the ball and slams it home to put Maryland up 29-25.
videos.headline: Fernando drives and crushes the rim

videos.description: Purdue's Mojel Eastern collects the steal and breaks the ankles of Darryl Morsell before finishing at the cup.
videos.headline: Eastern puts Morsell on skates

videos.description: Carsen Edwards shakes off his defender and hits a three, then later gets ahead for the fast break and flips it to Aaron Wheeler for two and a 57-54 Purdue lead.
videos.headline: Carsen hits clutch 3 to give Purdue lead
